to undertake in order to provide a drink for ten camels<b style="">.</b> The<span style="">&nbsp; </span>pitcher that she
carried upon her shoulders could not have been small<b style="">,</b> because the stone troughs that are near wells used by animals to
drink was not small<b style="">,</b> because you
don&#8217;t fill a trough for ten camels to drink with small sips of water<b style="">.</b> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

